  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Accessible WATSAN in Dist. Mansehra - HRDS</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The general aim of the project is to improve accessible services in district Mansehra through community based approaches.
This general aim is further broken up into four specific objectives which are:
1. To sensitize the service provider &amp; policy maker to adopt new approaches &amp; practices to promote accessible &amp; affordable local solutions for WATSON facilities.
2. To increase PWD&#x2019;s access to safe water &amp; sanitation facilities.
3. To ensure the participation of vulnerable population in design &amp; planning of WATSON schemes.
4. To mainstream the issue of disability in local development initiatives.</narrative>
  </description>
